text: Kutluyulovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Yakshimbetovsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 277 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Yermolayevo, 10 km from Yakshimbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Kutluyulovo
